title: WinRAR v5.1.0 32-bit and 64-bit with KEY
description:
This is the v5.1.0 final release of WinRAR in 32-bit and 64-bit
I've included a generic key with user name: USER
and unlimited company license.

Either install from same directory as the rarreg.key or copy/paste
into your winrar folder after installing. When you start winrar.exe
it will read the key.

There's really no need to use a keygen. There's no online
verification of the license, so there's no need to use different
credentials. Plus, every a/v program in the world thinks that the
keygen is malware.

Enjoy,
murph
